1
00:00:00,050 --> 00:00:01,662
A 20-year run has ended!

2
00:00:01,662 --> 00:00:09,237
A prominent blogger, Eric Goldman, has decided to pull the plug on Google AdSense for his websites, effective next year.

3
00:00:09,237 --> 00:00:17,050
After two decades, he's moving on from the platform, citing evolving ad tech and the diminishing returns of traditional display ads.

4
00:00:17,050 --> 00:00:23,375
It's a significant shift for a long-time user, highlighting changes in the digital advertising landscape.

